      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOGIE MAGIC (1) has a strong record this track and trip with 14 wins and five placings from 26 starts. Missed the frame latest (18.08) when seventh over 324m at this track in a Mix 2/3. Rates a leading player. DESPICABLE DASH (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (18.47) in a Mix 3/4 at this track. Has a good record here including nine wins. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and two minor placings from 11 starts. Bold showing expected. MISS LOUELLA (4) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (22.90) at Maitland. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. RAIDER DONKEY (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
